        <item>
            <title>Automate GitHub Pages with Travis CI</title>
            <link>https://richardstrnad.github.io/posts/2020/12/27/automate-github-pages-with-travis-ci/</link>
            <pubDate>Sun, 27 Dec 2020 21:30:39 +0100</pubDate>
            
            <guid>https://richardstrnad.github.io/posts/2020/12/27/automate-github-pages-with-travis-ci/</guid>
            <description>To have a CICD pipeline for my github pages site, i use the following travis config. GITHUB_AUTH_SECRET is set in the settings page of the respective travis project.
---install:- curl -LO https://github.com/gohugoio/hugo/releases/download/v${HUGO_RELEASE}/hugo_extended_${HUGO_RELEASE}_Linux-64bit.deb- sudo dpkg -i hugo*.debscript:- hugodeploy:- provider:pageslocal_dir:publicrepo:richardstrnad/richardstrnad.github.iotarget_branch:masterskip_cleanup:truegithub_token:$GITHUB_AUTH_SECRETkeep_history:trueon:branch:masterenv:global:- HUGO_RELEASE=0.</description>
            <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>To have a CICD pipeline for my github pages site, i use the following travis
config. GITHUB_AUTH_SECRET is set in the settings page of the respective travis
project.</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre style=";-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4"><code class="language-yml" data-lang="yml"><span style="color:#00f;font-weight:bold">---</span><span style="color:#bbb">
</span><span style="color:#bbb"></span><span style="color:#008000;font-weight:bold">install</span>:<span style="color:#bbb">
</span><span style="color:#bbb">  </span>- curl -LO https://github.com/gohugoio/hugo/releases/download/v${HUGO_RELEASE}/hugo_extended_${HUGO_RELEASE}_Linux-64bit.deb<span style="color:#bbb">
</span><span style="color:#bbb">  </span>- sudo dpkg -i hugo*.deb<span style="color:#bbb">
</span><span style="color:#bbb">
</span><span style="color:#bbb"></span><span style="color:#008000;font-weight:bold">script</span>:<span style="color:#bbb">
</span><span style="color:#bbb">  </span>- hugo<span style="color:#bbb">
</span><span style="color:#bbb">
</span><span style="color:#bbb"></span><span style="color:#008000;font-weight:bold">deploy</span>:<span style="color:#bbb">
</span><span style="color:#bbb">  </span>- <span style="color:#008000;font-weight:bold">provider</span>:<span style="color:#bbb"> </span>pages<span style="color:#bbb">
</span><span style="color:#bbb">    </span><span style="color:#008000;font-weight:bold">local_dir</span>:<span style="color:#bbb"> </span>public<span style="color:#bbb">
</span><span style="color:#bbb">    </span><span style="color:#008000;font-weight:bold">repo</span>:<span style="color:#bbb"> </span>richardstrnad/richardstrnad.github.io<span style="color:#bbb">
</span><span style="color:#bbb">    </span><span style="color:#008000;font-weight:bold">target_branch</span>:<span style="color:#bbb"> </span>master<span style="color:#bbb">
</span><span style="color:#bbb">    </span><span style="color:#008000;font-weight:bold">skip_cleanup</span>:<span style="color:#bbb"> </span><span style="color:#008000;font-weight:bold">true</span><span style="color:#bbb">
</span><span style="color:#bbb">    </span><span style="color:#008000;font-weight:bold">github_token</span>:<span style="color:#bbb"> </span>$GITHUB_AUTH_SECRET<span style="color:#bbb">
</span><span style="color:#bbb">    </span><span style="color:#008000;font-weight:bold">keep_history</span>:<span style="color:#bbb"> </span><span style="color:#008000;font-weight:bold">true</span><span style="color:#bbb">
</span><span style="color:#bbb">    </span><span style="color:#008000;font-weight:bold">on</span>:<span style="color:#bbb">
</span><span style="color:#bbb">      </span><span style="color:#008000;font-weight:bold">branch</span>:<span style="color:#bbb"> </span>master<span style="color:#bbb">
</span><span style="color:#bbb">
</span><span style="color:#bbb"></span><span style="color:#008000;font-weight:bold">env</span>:<span style="color:#bbb">
</span><span style="color:#bbb">  </span><span style="color:#008000;font-weight:bold">global</span>:<span style="color:#bbb">
</span><span style="color:#bbb">    </span>- HUGO_RELEASE=0.79.1<span style="color:#bbb">
</span></code></pre></div>]]></content>
